title: The Spookers
author: steffwo
pages:
#- Once upon a poop there was a poop that spooped the spooky spookers on the village of fart. It was a windy night that smelled like fresh fart that could come from my dead grandpa's butthole. Every day the spooky poop spooped the spookers so they stopped
#- spooking the villagers on village of fart. The spookers moved to shitsville where they had tons of spooky scary times. But they were kinda sad that it didn't smell fart in shitsville. Instead, it smelled like shit. Well poop, said the super spooker.
#- Super spooker was the spooking boss in their spooky cult. Suddenly a member farted and the instantly killed him. Everyone got in a bad mood from that incident and their group fell apart. The end.
#- 